00:34:39.669 --> 00:34:43.465
what are the considerations? You know? Exactly.

794
00:34:43.465 --> 00:34:46.502
It would be interesting, but in the interim

795
00:34:46.502 --> 00:34:49.404
I think this, like you say, the out of body experience

796
00:34:49.404 --> 00:34:53.386
seems to be a way to go to a higher dialogue

797
00:34:53.386 --> 00:34:54.451
within the being.

798
00:34:54.451 --> 00:34:57.574
And as you have, your people that you have studied,

799
00:34:57.574 --> 00:35:00.918
have said, and also as the people Raymond have studied

800
00:35:00.918 --> 00:35:04.587
came back with this, probably the one significant thing

801
00:35:04.587 --> 00:35:06.990
is the whole notion of love.

802
00:35:06.990 --> 00:35:10.333
<v ->Sure, yeah, I mean people come back with</v>

