00:35:15.732 --> 00:35:18.739
I don't know if it ruins CEOs to have

806
00:35:18.739 --> 00:35:20.434
a near-death experience or not.

807
00:35:20.434 --> 00:35:23.139
<v Voiceover>Maybe it would make them a more conscious CEO.</v>

808
00:35:23.139 --> 00:35:24.832
<v ->Well, it would depend on the company, you know.</v>

